## ✅ Conclusion

The analysis reveals a gap between **financial success and operational efficiency**. While revenue performance is strong, inefficiencies in patient flow negatively impact service quality.

This project demonstrates how data analytics can support **strategic decision-making and operational improvement in healthcare systems**.

